    <h2 class="cag-h2">Did Real Buyers Pick a Sex — or Pick a Bird?</h2>
    <p>Rather than us condensing ten years of male-or-female emails, hear it from two buyers who made the call. Notice what neither of them agonized over: whether they were getting a cock or a hen. Each chose the bird whose temperament fit their home and let the DNA certificate fill in the sex — and dozens more verified accounts live on our <a href="/african-grey-reviews/">buyer review wall</a>.</p>
